GeneralComments:
$10 for 3pin 10amp daytime charging and can use amenities (toilets, kitchen). Short term 3pin 10amp $2/hour if don't use amenities. 10amp charging park by Office (see photo of plugged in car). Powered campsite $20 for 24 hours 16 amp blue commando (stay the night; cost for unit is extra $25/person). EFTPOS available.
Come for casual daytime charging (go for a beautiful hike up colonial knob, entrance is just meters away) and Low cost accommodation (bring own bedding). 10-15 min walking distance to restaurants, shopping mall, aquatic centre, ten pin bowling, go karts, Pataka Museum, railway. Information at http://www.campelsdon.co.nz/phone/casual-bookings.html
